# Title: OneLogin User Account Locked
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-10-12
# Level: low
# Description: Detects when an user account is locked or suspended.
# MITRE Tactic: Impact
# Tags: attack.impact
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/identity/onelogin/onelogin_user_account_locked.yml
# False Positives:
#   - System may lock or suspend user accounts.

event_type_id IN (532, 553, 551)